<lb ed="P" n="0236b03"/>切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>嶄</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0303" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">士銜切嶄巖也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>獠</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0310" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">盧皓切西南夷名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>聻</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0318" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">尼止切指物貌</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>閬</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0325" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">音浪</note>。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="P" n="0236b04"/><entry><form>摵</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0402" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">所責切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>浹</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0406" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">子叶切洽也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>嚚</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0412" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">魚巾切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB01036">𥈅</g></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0416" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">他典切與靦同</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>睍</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP155p0236b0423" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">胡典
<lb ed="P" n="0236b05"/>切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
